item.title: CVE-2022-33936|2024-09-17T02:57:19.617Z -- dell -- cloud%20mobility%20for%20dell%20storage
item.description: Cloud Mobility for Dell EMC Storage, 1.3.0.XXX contains a RCE vulnerability. A non-privileged user could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to achieving a root shell. This is a critical issue; so Dell recommends customers to upgrade at the earliest opportunity.
